=3D"mi"><use data-c=3D"1D6FF" xlink:href=3D"#MJX-TEX-I-1D6FF"></use></g><g =
data-mml-node=3D"mo" transform=3D"translate(444,0)"><use data-c=3D"28" xlin=
k:href=3D"#MJX-TEX-N-28"></use></g><g data-mml-node=3D"mi" transform=3D"tra=
